# ViperSQL — SQL database server written in Zia
project vipersql
version 0.2.0
lang zia
entry vipersql.zia

# === Package Metadata ===
package-name ViperSQL
package-description "SQL database server with PostgreSQL wire protocol compatibility"
package-identifier org.viper-lang.vipersql

# === Assets ===
asset docs docs
asset README.md .

# === File Associations ===
file-assoc .sql "SQL Script" application/sql

# === Shortcuts ===
shortcut-menu on
